	<Fixlet>
		<Title>MS02-048: Flaw in Certificate Enrollment Control Could Allow Deletion of Digital Certificates - Windows XP</Title>
		<Description><![CDATA[
Microsoft has released a patch eliminating a security vulnerability in Windows XP. The vulnerability results from a flaw in Certificate Enrollment Control, an ActiveX control responsible for enrolling web-based certificates. A malicious user can launch a denial of service attack by deleting or corrupting digital certificates on a user's system. This patch eliminates the vulnerability by upgrading the Certificate Enrollment Control.<BR><BR><b>Note:</b> Affected computers will report back as 'Fixed' once the patch has run successfully, but the vulnerability will not be closed until the affected computer is restarted. <BR><BR><b>Note:</b> This patch is included in Windows XP Service Pack 1.<BR><BR><b>File Size:</b> 276 KB
]]></Description>
		<Relevance>(if( name of operating system starts with "Win" ) then platform id of operating system != 3 else false) AND (if exists property "in proxy agent context" then ( not in proxy agent context ) else true )</Relevance>
		<Relevance>(language of version block of file "kernel32.dll" of system folder contains "English") OR (exists value of key "HKLM\System\CurrentControlSet\Control\Nls\MUILanguages" of registry)</Relevance>
		<Relevance>not exists key "HKLM\Software\Wow6432Node\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion" whose (exists value "ProductId" of it OR exists value "CommonFilesDir" of it) of registry AND not exists values "PROCESSOR_ARCHITECTURE" whose (it as string as lowercase = "ia64") of keys "HKLM\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Session Manager\Environment" of registry</Relevance>
		<Relevance>((name of it = "WinXP") AND (service pack major version of it = 0)) of operating system</Relevance>
		<Relevance>not exists key "HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\Software\Microsoft\Updates\Windows XP\SP1\Q323172" of registry</Relevance>
		<Relevance>not exists key "HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Updates\Windows XP\SP1\Q324720" of registry</Relevance>
		<Relevance>not exists key "HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Updates\Windows XP\SP2\KB811113" of registry</Relevance>
